<HTML>

<HEAD>
<TITLE>Placer Dome - One World</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="ffffff" link="52001f" vlink="858585">

	<a href=#00>
	<img src="../gfx/pdlogosm.gif" alt="Placer Dome banner gif" border=0></a>
	<br>

	<table border=0>
	
	<tr>
	
	<td valign=top>
	<a href="../gfx/00butbar.map">
	<img src="../gfx/00a.gif"  valign=top alt="Button links - image mapped gif" border=0 align=left ismap></a>
	
	<br>
	
	</td>

	
	<td valign=top>
	
	<img src="../gfx/1world.jpg" alt="One World photo illustration">
	<p>
	
	
	Social and economic demands for commercial products and services have created a
	conflict between the industrialized world and nature. One of the biggest challenges we
	face is the need to protect the environment for the enjoyment of future
	generations while maintaining the high standards of living which threaten it. 
	<p>
		
	<img src="../gfx/costaric.jpg" alt="Costa Rican jungle jpeg" align=right vspace=10 hspace=10>
	<p>	

	At Placer Dome, our environmental management programme and environmental policies
	guide our daily operations. Through effective communication and cooperation,
	these policies will help preserve the most precious commodity of all: the natural
	environment.
	<p>
    
    <a href="03e.html">Spelling It Out (the policy)</a>
	<br>
	<a href="03f.html">We Declare (the principles)</a>
	<p>
	
	<font size=+1>
	<strong>
	<a href="03b.html">
	Keeping it Clean: Minimizing Enviro-impact</a>
	</strong>
	</font>
	<br>
	Environmental management is an integral part of the operations at every Placer Dome
	site. Like any machine with moving parts, the entire system must be kept clean and
	maintained regularly in order to work at its best.
	<p>
   
    
	<font size=+1>
	<strong>
	<a href="03c.html">
	Reclamation: Last, But Never Least</a>
	</strong>
	</font>
	<br>
	Once mines are operational, reclamation activities become an ongoing process
	and may commence as early as the first year of operation. 
	<p>

	<font size=+1>
	<strong>
	<a href="03d.html">
	The Human Factor: Protecting People</a>
	</strong>
	</font>
	<br>
	Regardless of how big an organization becomes, its success is dependent upon the
	individuals associated with it. The health and safety of Placer Dome's employees,
	contractors and relevant publics are always the priority.
	<p>
	
	<a href="03g.html">
	<img src="../gfx/03turtl.gif" align=left hspace=8 border=0 alt="Aboriginal illustration of a turtle"></a>
   
   <br>
   
    <font size=+1>
	<strong>
	<a href="03g.html">
	Our Commitment to Aboriginal People</a>
	</strong>
	</font>
	
	<br>
	Placer Dome Canada is committed to creating and maintaining a 
	relationship with Aboriginal peoples based on trust and respect.
	
	
	 
      

	</td>
	
	</table>

    <br><br>
		
