<HTML>

<HEAD>
<TITLE>One World - Spelling It Out</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="ffffff" link="52001f" vlink="858585">

	<a href=#00>
	<img src="../gfx/pdlogosm.gif" alt="Placer Dome banner gif" border=0></a>
	<br>

	<table border=0>
	
	<tr>
	
	<td valign=top>
	
	<a href="../gfx/00butbar.map">
	<img src="../gfx/00a.gif" alt="Button links - image mapped gif" border=0 align=left ismap></a></td>
	<br>
	

	<td valign=top>
	
	<h2>
 	We Declare (the principles) 
	</h2>
	
	<a href="03a.html">
	Back to "One World"</a>
	<p>
	
	<img src="../gfx/03declar.jpg" align=right alt="Forest picture, environmental protection" hspace=20 vspace=3>


	Demonstrated environmental leadership is a dominant component of our drive for success.
	Even though our policies are some of the strongest in the mining industry, a further
	declaration of principles was adopted in 1995 to improve the application of the
	policies and to monitor their effectiveness.
	<p>
	
	To establish a position of environmental leadership, Placer Dome will achieve and
	maintain the level of performance and practice which, in the conduct of all of its
	activities, will:
	<p>
	
	<ul>
	
	<li type=bullet> Protect human health
	<p>

	<li type=bullet> Minimize use of the surrounding ecosystem
	<p>

	<li type=bullet> Return sites to a state compatible with a healthy and safe environment
	<p>
	

	</ul>
	<br>
	
	By adhering to these principles Placer Dome hopes to reduce the effects of its
	operations on both the modern and natural environment. In addition, we hope that our
	efforts can and will be modelled by others in similar industries.</td>
	
	</table>
	
	<p>
		
	<a name="00">
	<table border=0></a>
	<tr>
	
	<td width=120></td>
	
	
	<td>	
