	<a href="../07numb/07a.html">
	Numbers</a> |
	<a href="../05tech/05a.html">
	Tools</a> |	
	<a href="08a.html">
	Sites</a> |
	<a href="../06faq/06a.html">
	FAQ & Glossary</a> |
	<a href="../09latest/09a.html">
	Latest</a>
	<br>
	
	<font size=-1>
	<a href="../index.html">
	Home Page</a> |
	<a href="mailto:goldpanner@placerdome.com">
	E-mail</a> |
	<a href="../10index/10a.html">
