    <p>

	
    <h2>Placer Dome moves to more than 50% ownership
      of Highlands Gold - tomorrow last day to accept</h2>
	
    <strong>January 16, 1997</strong>
    
    <p>

     <strong>Vancouver, Canada</strong> - Placer Dome Inc. now owns more than 50% of
     Highlands Gold Limited.  Friday is the final business day for
     Highlands shareholders to accept the Placer Dome offer of A$0.75 per
     share, which is scheduled to close on Saturday, January 18 at
     midnight.
    <p>
        "We are pleased with the level of acceptances we have received to
     date and we are looking forward to our offer closing on Saturday,"
     John Willson, President and CEO, said.  "We are still processing
     acceptances as they flood in."


    <p>
    For further information:<br>
    Investor Relations: Earl Dunlop (604) 661-3779<br>
	Media Relations: Hugh Leggatt (604) 661-1554<br>
       
    
