<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Clemson University Graduate School Home
Page</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<Body background=/images/back1.gif>
<center><IMG ALIGN=middle
SRC="http://www.clemson.edu/curedesign/graphics/cuheader.gif"><P>
<img src="/images/gs-logo.gif"><P>
<img src="/images/homepage.gif"></center><p>

<Font size=+1><B><I>WELCOME</Font></I> to the Clemson
University Graduate
School's Home
Page.  The information which follows is made available to provide
graduate students with
up-to-date information and to provide prospective students with a
broad knowledge of the
myriad of opportunities for study at the graduate level.  Many of
the questions that you may
have will be answered here, and for unanswered questions, we
direct you to specific
departments or individuals...<P>
We appreciate your interest in Clemson. We hope that our
University has the program of
study which you desire to pursue.  We look forward to receiving
your completed application.</B>
