AP EC 719	PROFESSIONAL PROBLEMS IN AGRIBUSINESS MANAGEMENT
	3 cr. (3 and 0) F
	Concepts and principles of agribusiness firm management; decision theory, information 
systems, systems analysis and organization theory applied to the organization, administration 
and management of agriculturally related businesses.

AP EC 800	HISTORY OF ECONOMIC THOUGHT
(ECON 800)	3 cr. (3 and 0)
