	1-3 cr. (1-3 and 0)

AG ED 631	METHODS IN ENVIRONMENTAL EDUCATION
	3 cr. (3 and 0) SS

AG ED 632	VISUAL MEDIA FOR AGRIBUSINESS
	3 cr. (2 and 3) S

